{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality."}],"metadata":{"title":"handleOpenURL:","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handleOpenURL:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSURL","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSURL"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"url","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"url","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The URL to process.","type":"text"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"YES if the URL was handled by Pushwoosh, NO otherwise."}]}],"kind":"content"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handles special Pushwoosh URLs, primarily used for:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Test device registration"}]},{"text":": Register device for push testing via QR code","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Deep link tracking"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Process tracked deep links from push notifications","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Should be called from your app’s URL handling methods. Returns YES if the URL"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"was a Pushwoosh URL and was handled, NO if it should be processed by your app.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Example","type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Handle URLs in SceneDelegate (iOS 13+):","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class SceneDelegate: UIResponder, UIWindowSceneDelegate {","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, openURLContexts URLContexts: Set<UIOpenURLContext>) {","        guard let url = URLContexts.first?.url else { return }","","        \/\/ First, check if Pushwoosh handles this URL","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            Logger.info(\"URL handled by Pushwoosh\")","            return","        }","","        \/\/ Handle other deep links","        DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, continue userActivity: NSUserActivity) {","        guard userActivity.activityType == NSUserActivityTypeBrowsingWeb,","              let url = userActivity.webpageURL else { return }","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return","        }","","        UniversalLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}","","\/\/ Legacy AppDelegate support","class AppDelegate: UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ app: UIApplication,","                    open url: URL,","                    options: [UIApplication.OpenURLOptionsKey: Any] = [:]) -> Bool {","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return true","        }","","        return DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/handleOpenURL:":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:","title":"handleOpenURL:","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection","type":"topic","title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"}}}